  "description": "<p>Sleep warm without weighing down your pack. The VectAir UL 4S Insulated Sleeping Pad uses 200 grams of Hyperloft synthetic insulation to create a barrier between you the chilly ground below. Thanks to an R-value of 5.4 it&rsquo;s plenty comfortable for 4-season use, and the included pump sack makes inflation a breeze.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Made of lightweight 30-denier brushed polyester ripstop with an internal TPU laminate and welded seams to keep the pad air-tight</li>\n<li>Internal mylar film reflects heat back to you</li>\n<li>Offset dot welds eliminate cold spots</li>\n<li>200g of HyperLoft synthetic insulation is lightweight and warm</li>\n<li>Low-profile recessed valve creates a smooth sleeping surface</li>\n<li>Roll-top pump sack inflates quickly and has enough extra room to store a compact pillow or sleeping clothes</li>\n<li>Hook-and-loop strap keeps the pad rolled for storage</li>\n<li>Pump sack and repair kit included</li>\n</ul>",
